name: RTCIceCandidate.foundation
description: The RTCIceCandidate interface's read-only foundation property is a string which uniquely identifies the candidate across multiple transports.
content: The RTCIceCandidate interface's read-only foundation property is a string which uniquely identifies the candidate across multiple transports. As such, the foundation can be used to correlate candidates that are present on multiple RTCIceTransport objects
